Source: lernstick-speech-dispatcher
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ronny Standtke <ronny.standtke@gmx.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), config-package-dev
Standards-Version: 3.7.3

Package: lernstick-speech-dispatcher
Architecture: all
Depends: libttspico-utils, orca, sox, speech-dispatcher-pico
Provides: ${diverted-files}
Conflicts: ${diverted-files}
Description: reconfigures speech-dispatcher to use pico as default
 The default tts engine of speech-dispatcher (espeak) sounds really terrible.
 Therefore we change the default to pico. We also use the play command of sox
 to improve the dull output quality of pico.
